tathatāṃ śūnyatāṃ gataḥ tathāgataḥ | atha vā yathā te tathāgatā gatā gacchanti gamiṣyanti tathā gacchatīti tathāgataḥ | taṃ tathāgataṃ praṇamyeti pūrveṇa saṃbandhaḥ |

<commentary>agrataḥ sthito bhūtvā kṛtāñjalipuṭaḥ san bhagavān vajradhara idam āha—maddhitāyetyādi | mahyaṃ hitaṃ maddhitaṃ hitam āyatipathyam āgāmiparṇāmatvāt || mamārthāya matprayojanāya me mama he vibho anukampāya anugrahāya yathā yena prakāreṇāhaṃ lābhī bhavāmi | kasyeti āha | māyājālābhisaṃbhodher iti | māyājālābhisaṃbodhir nāma kramas tasya yathāhaṃ lābhī bhavāmi tathā bhagavān prakāśayatv iti vakṣyamāṇena kriyāpadena saṃbandhaḥ ||</commentary>

ajñānapaṅkamagnānāṃ sarvasattvānāṃ hitāya ca | tatrājñānam avidyā saivāsaṅgasthānatvād duruttaratvāc ca paṅka iva paṅkaḥ | tasmin magnā ye satvās teṣām hitāya ||
